{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_RuEPnLOsjaSnauwVvx6OvF3Z","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"tool_SPCVf4ry7GW8G9G1zonJulEx","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Refine tasklist for TST-001","prompt":"You are the tasklist-refiner agent for ticket TST-001.\n\n## Your Task\nRead the following artifacts and generate a detailed, implementation-ready tasklist at `aidd/docs/tasklist/TST-001.md`.\n\n## Source Artifacts (READ THESE FIRST)\n1. PRD: `/Users/griogrii_riabov/grigorii_projects/ai_advent_challenge_new/aidd/docs/prd/TST-001.prd.md` - Status: READY, uses Polling (30s interval)\n2. Plan: `/Users/griogrii_riabov/grigorii_projects/ai_advent_challenge_new/aidd/docs/plan/TST-001.md` - Status: READY, uses SSE for live role sync (final implementation decision)\n3. Spec: `/Users/griogrii_riabov/grigorii_projects/ai_advent_challenge_new/aidd/docs/spec/TST-001.spec.yaml` - Status: draft (outdated - uses WebSocket)\n4. Current tasklist: `/Users/griogrii_riabov/grigorii_projects/ai_advent_challenge_new/aidd/docs/tasklist/TST-001.md` - Template with placeholders\n\n## Key Implementation Decisions (from PRD and Plan)\n- **Backend**: Custom WebFlux filter for RBAC (no Spring Security)\n- **Auth**: X-Profile-Key header-based\n- **Frontend**: React + Zustand\n- **Session Sync**: SSE (Server-Sent Events) - NOT WebSocket, NOT Polling\n- **Cache**: Caffeine with 5min TTL\n- **Audit**: PostgreSQL table `rbac_audit_log`\n\n## Output Requirements\nReplace the template tasklist with a fully detailed one containing:\n1. **AIDD:CONTEXT_PACK** - Updated TL;DR, scope, boundaries, decisions, test policy\n2. **AIDD:SPEC_PACK** - Goal, non-goals, key decisions, risks\n3. **AIDD:TEST_STRATEGY** - Unit, integration, e2e scopes\n4. **AIDD:TEST_EXECUTION** - Concrete commands and filters\n5. **AIDD:ITERATIONS_FULL** - At least 4 detailed iterations (I1-I4):\n   - I1: Database migration + RBAC domain model\n   - I2: RBAC WebFilter + Audit logging service\n   - I3: Profile service integration + Role caching\n   - I4: Frontend SSE integration + useRoleGuard hook\n   - I5: SSE endpoint + Role events (optional but recommended)\n6. **AIDD:NEXT_3** - First 3 iteration pointers\n\nEach iteration must have:\n- iteration_id, Goal, Outputs, DoD, Boundaries\n- Expected paths, Size budget (max_files, max_loc)\n- Steps (detailed), Tests (profile, tasks, filters)\n- Acceptance mapping to AC-1, AC-2, AC-3, AC-4\n\n## Critical Rules\n- Use the Plan as the source of truth for implementation details\n- The Spec is outdated (draft) - use PRD + Plan decisions\n- Set Status to READY when done\n- Do NOT ask the user questions - synthesize from artifacts\n\nWrite the complete tasklist file to `aidd/docs/tasklist/TST-001.md`.","subagent_type":"feature-dev-aidd:tasklist-refiner"}}],"model":"kimi-for-coding","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":47473,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available","prompt_tokens":47473,"cached_tokens":0},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3bb52f18-577c-4498-9d63-c3d743a62879","uuid":"c8c699b3-380d-4d96-bc51-e4893ab6a00b"}
