ers\n5. **AIDD:ITERATIONS_FULL** - At least 4 detailed iterations (I1-I4):\n   - I1: Database migration + RBAC domain model\n   - I2: RBAC WebFilter + Audit logging service\n   - I3: Profile service integration + Role caching\n   - I4: Frontend SSE integration + useRoleGuard hook\n   - I5: SSE endpoint + Role events (optional but recommended)\n6. **AIDD:NEXT_3** - First 3 iteration pointers\n\nEach iteration must have:\n- iteration_id, Goal, Outputs, DoD, Boundaries\n- Expected paths, Size budget (max_files, max_loc)\n- Steps (detailed), Tests (profile, tasks, filters)\n- Acceptance mapping to AC-1, AC-2, AC-3, AC-4\n\n## Critical Rules\n- Use the Plan as the source of truth for implementation details\n- The Spec is outdated (draft) - use PRD + Plan decisions\n- Set Status to READY when done\n- Do NOT ask the user questions - synthesize from artifacts\n\nWrite the complete tasklist file to `aidd/docs/tasklist/TST-001.md`.","agentId":"a4339a688a6744112","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The tasklist has been successfully created. Here is a summary of what was generated:\n\n## Summary: TST-001 Tasklist Created\n\n**Status:** READY\n\n### Key Implementation Decisions Applied (from PRD + Plan)\n\n| Aspect | Decision | Source |\n|--------|----------|--------|\n| **Backend** | Custom WebFlux filter for RBAC (no Spring Security) | Plan |\n| **Auth** | X-Profile-Key header-based | PRD Q2 |\n| **Frontend** | React + Zustand | PRD Q3 |\n| **Session Sync** | SSE (Server-Sent Events) | Plan (overrides PRD polling) |\n| **Cache** | Caffeine with 5min TTL | Plan |\n| **Audit** | PostgreSQL table `rbac_audit_log` | PRD Q4 |\n\n### Iterations Defined (5 total)\n\n| Iteration | Goal | Size Budget | Acceptance Criteria |\n|-----------|------|-------------|---------------------|\n| **I1** | Database migration + RBAC domain model | 10 files, 500 LOC | AC-2 (audit log structure) |\n| **I2** | RBAC WebFilter + Audit logging service | 8 files, 800 LOC | AC-1 (403 responses), AC-2 |\n| **I3** | Profile service integration + Role caching | 6 files, 400 LOC | AC-4 (P95 ≤ 10ms) |\n| **I4** | Frontend SSE integration + useRoleGuard hook | 4 files, 300 LOC | AC-3 (5s sync) |\n| **I5** | SSE endpoint + Role events | 5 files, 400 LOC | AC-3, AC-2 |\n\n### NEXT_3 Pointer List\n1. **I1**: Database migration + RBAC domain model\n2. **I2**: RBAC WebFilter + Audit logging service  \n3. **I3**: Profile service integration + Role caching\n\n### Important Notes\n- The **Spec is outdated** (uses WebSocket) — the tasklist follows the Plan which uses SSE\n- **Spec is draft status** and was not used as a source of truth\n- All PRD decisions Q1-Q5 have been incorporated\n- Each iteration includes detailed steps, tests, exit criteria, and risk mitigations\n\nThe tasklist is now ready for implementation at `/Users/griogrii_riabov/grigorii_projects/ai_advent_challenge_new/aidd/docs/tasklist/TST-001.md`."}],"totalDurationMs":216963,"totalTokens":43594,"totalToolUseCount":5,"usage":{"input_tokens":6973,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":36096,"output_tokens":525,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
