ook tests pass","+    - Component renders correctly with/without role","+    - Store updates trigger re-renders","+    - Refactored AdminRoles works as before","+  - Steps:","+    - Add roleVersion and SSE subscription to profileStore","+    - Create useRoleGuard hook with memoized checks","+    - Create RoleGuard component with fallback support","+    - Refactor AdminRoles to use useRoleGuard","+    - Write tests for useRoleGuard hook","+    - Write tests for RoleGuard component","+  - Tests:","+    - profile: targeted","+    - tasks: `npm test -- useRoleGuard`","+    - filters: `useRoleGuard.test.ts`, `RoleGuard.test.tsx`","+  - Acceptance mapping: AC-3 (5s sync)","+  - Risks & mitigations:","+    - SSE connection errors → Auto-reconnect with exponential backoff","+    - Memory leaks on unmount → Proper cleanup in useEffect","+  - Dependencies: I3"," ","-### I5: SSE endpoint + Role events (iteration_id: I5)","-- parent_iteration_id: I4","-- Goal: Implement backend SSE endpoint for role change notifications and role assignment service","-- Outputs:","-  - `RoleEventService.java` — SSE event management with Sinks.Many","-  - `RoleEventsController.java` — SSE endpoint /api/profiles/role-events","-  - `RoleAssignmentService.java` — Role assignment with cache invalidation and events","-  - `RoleChangeEvent.java` — Event record for role changes","-- DoD:","-  - SSE endpoint accepts namespace, reference, channel, token params","-  - Role change events broadcast to connected clients","-  - Cache invalidated on role assignment/revocation","-  - Audit log written for GRANT/REVOKE operations","-- Boundaries:","-  - Reuse existing SSE pattern from flow events","-  - Heartbeat every 30 seconds","-  - Proper cleanup on disconnect","-- Priority: medium","-- Blocking: false","-- deps: [I4]","-- locks: []","-- Expected paths:","-  - `backend-mcp/src/main/java/com/aiadvent/mcp/backend/rbac/service/RoleEventService.java`","-  - `backend-mcp/src/main/java/com/aiadvent/mcp/backend/rbac/controller/RoleEventsController.java`","-  - `backend-mcp/src/main/java/com/aiadvent/mcp/backend/rbac/service/RoleAssignmentService.java`","-- Size budget:","-  - max_files: 5","-  - max_loc: 400","-- Commands:","-  - `./gradlew :backend-mcp:test --tests \"*RoleEventsControllerTest*\"`","-  - `./gradlew :backend-mcp:test --tests \"*RoleAssignmentServiceTest*\"`","-- Exit criteria:","-  - SSE endpoint tests pass","-  - Role assignment service tests pass","-  - End-to-end test: role change → SSE notification received","-- Steps:","-  1. Create RoleChangeEvent record","-  2. Create RoleEventService with subscriber management","-  3. Create RoleEventsController with SSE endpoint","-  4. Implement heartbeat flux (30s interval)","-  5. Create RoleAssignmentService","-  6. Implement assignRole with cache invalidation","-  7. Implement revokeRole with cache invalidation","-  8. Integrate audit logging for GRANT/REVOKE","-  9. Write controller tests for SSE endpoint","-  10. Write service tests for role assignment","-- Tests:","-  - profile: full","-  - tasks: `./gradlew :backend-mcp:test --tests \"*RoleEvent*\" --tests \"*RoleAssignment*\"`","-  - filters: `shouldBroadcastRoleChange`, `shouldInvalidateCacheOnAssign`","-- Acceptance mapping: AC-3 (live role sync), AC-2 (audit for GRANT/REVOKE)","-- Risks & mitigations:","-  - Risk: Memory leak from stale subscribers → Mitigation: doOnCancel/doOnTerminate cleanup","-  - Risk: SSE backpressure → Mitigation: onBackpressureBuffer strategy","-- Dependencies: I4 (frontend SSE integration)","+- [ ] I5: SSE endpoint + Role events (iteration_id: I5)","+  - parent_iteration_id: I4","+  - Goal: Backend SSE endpoint for role change notifications and role assignment service","+  - Outputs:","+    - `RoleEventService.java` — SSE event management with Sinks","+    - `RoleEventsController.java` — SSE endpoint controller","+    - `RoleAssignmentService.java` — Role assignment with notifications","+  - DoD:","+    - SSE endpoint at `/api/pr