{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"tool_TtgSaYgCLCTycBBhXoiQARUr","type":"tool_result","content":"--- /Users/griogrii_riabov/grigorii_projects/ai_advent_challenge_new/aidd/docs/tasklist/TST-001.md\n+++ /Users/griogrii_riabov/grigorii_projects/ai_advent_challenge_new/aidd/docs/tasklist/TST-001.md\n@@ -434,12 +434,9 @@\n \n ## AIDD:NEXT_3\n > 3 ближайших implement‑чекбокса. Pointer list: 1–2 строки и `ref:` на детализацию.\n-- [ ] I1: Database migration + RBAC domain model — Create rbac_audit_log table and domain classes (ref: iteration_id=I1)\n-- [ ] I2: RBAC WebFilter + Audit logging service — Implement WebFlux filter for mutation API protection (ref: iteration_id=I2)\n-- [ ] I3: Profile service integration + Role caching — Integrate profile client with Caffeine cache (ref: iteration_id=I3)\n-\n----\n-\n+- archived: (ref: iteration_id=I2)\n+- archived: (ref: iteration_id=I3)\n+- [ ] I1: Database migration + RBAC domain model (ref: iteration_id=I1)\n ## AIDD:OUT_OF_SCOPE_BACKLOG\n > Побочные идеи/задачи, которые НЕ входят в текущий work_item (без расширения scope).\n - [ ] Redis distributed cache for roles (source: research)\n@@ -452,20 +449,17 @@\n ## AIDD:HANDOFF_INBOX\n > Сюда падают задачи из Research/Review/QA (с source: aidd/reports/...).\n \n+\n+---\n+\n <!-- handoff:manual start -->\n <!-- handoff:manual end -->\n-\n----\n-\n ## AIDD:QA_TRACEABILITY\n > AC → check → result → evidence.\n-- AC-1: All POST/PUT/DELETE APIs return 403 for unauthorized users → I2 tests → not-verified → TBD\n-- AC-2: All role operations logged to rbac_audit_log → I1, I2, I5 tests → not-verified → TBD\n-- AC-3: Frontend role guards update within 5 seconds of backend change → I4, I5 tests → not-verified → TBD\n-- AC-4: RBAC latency P95 ≤ 10ms under 1000 RPS load → I3 tests → not-verified → TBD\n-\n----\n-\n+- AC-1 -> <check> -> not-verified -> TBD\n+- AC-2 -> <check> -> not-verified -> TBD\n+- AC-3 -> <check> -> not-verified -> TBD\n+- AC-4 -> <check> -> not-verified -> TBD\n ## AIDD:CHECKLIST\n \n ### AIDD:CHECKLIST_SPEC\n@@ -499,8 +493,7 @@\n > Формат записи:\n > `- YYYY-MM-DD source=implement id=I4 kind=iteration hash=abc123 link=aidd/reports/tests/<ticket>/TST-001.jsonl msg=short-note`\n \n----\n-\n+- (empty)\n ## AIDD:HOW_TO_UPDATE\n - Правило итерации: **1 чекбокс** (или 2 тесно связанных) — затем Stop.\n - Отмечайте чекбоксы так:\n[tasklist-check] merged 4 QA traceability entries\n[tasklist-check] dropped 1 invalid progress entries\n[tasklist-check] rebuilt AIDD:NEXT_3","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3bb52f18-577c-4498-9d63-c3d743a62879","uuid":"af0b66ba-f671-46ce-a00b-2d124e3f9da0","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"--- /Users/griogrii_riabov/grigorii_projects/ai_advent_challenge_new/aidd/docs/tasklist/TST-001.md\n+++ /Users/griogrii_riabov/grigorii_projects/ai_advent_challenge_new/aidd/docs/tasklist/TST-001.md\n@@ -434,12 +434,9 @@\n \n ## AIDD:NEXT_3\n > 3 ближайших implement‑чекбокса. Pointer list: 1–2 строки и `ref:` на детализацию.\n-- [ ] I1: Database migration + RBAC domain model — Create rbac_audit_log table and domain classes (ref: iteration_id=I1)\n-- [ ] I2: RBAC WebFilter + Audit logging service — Implement WebFlux filter for mutation API protection (ref: iteration_id=I2)\n-- [ ] I3: Profile service integration + Role caching — Integrate profile client with Caffeine cache (ref: iteration_id=I3)\n-\n----\n-\n+- archived: (ref: iteration_id=I2)\n+- archived: (ref: iteration_id=I3)\n+- [ ] I1: Database migration + RBAC domain model (ref: iteration_id=I1)\n ## AIDD:OUT_OF_SCOPE_BACKLOG\n > Побочные идеи/задачи, которые НЕ входят в текущий work_item (без расширения scope).\n - [ ] Redis distributed cache for roles (source: research)\n@@ -452,20 +449,17 @@\n ## AIDD:HANDOFF_INBOX\n > Сюда падают задачи из Research/Review/QA (с source: aidd/reports/...).\n \n+\n+---\n+\n <!-- handoff:manual start -->\n <!-- handoff:manual end -->\n-\n----\n-\n ## AIDD:QA_TRACEABILITY\n > AC → check → result → evidence.\n-- AC-1: All POST/PUT/DELETE APIs return 403 for unauthorized users → I2 tests → not-verified → TBD\n-- AC-2: All role operations logged to rbac_audit_log → I1, I2, I5 tests → not-verified → TBD\n-- AC-3: Frontend role guards update within 5 seconds of backend change → I4, I5 tests → not-verified → TBD\n-- AC-4: RBAC latency P95 ≤ 10ms under 1000 RPS load → I3 tests → not-verified → TBD\n-\n----\n-\n+- AC-1 -> <check> -> not-verified -> TBD\n+- AC-2 -> <check> -> not-verified -> TBD\n+- AC-3 -> <check> -> not-verified -> TBD\n+- AC-4 -> <check> -> not-verified -> TBD\n ## AIDD:CHECKLIST\n \n ### AIDD:CHECKLIST_SPEC\n@@ -499,8 +493,7 @@\n > Формат записи:\n > `- YYYY-MM-DD source=implement id=I4 kind=iteration hash=abc123 link=aidd/reports/tests/<ticket>/TST-001.jsonl msg=short-note`\n \n----\n-\n+- (empty)\n ## AIDD:HOW_TO_UPDATE\n - Правило итерации: **1 чекбокс** (или 2 тесно связанных) — затем Stop.\n - Отмечайте чекбоксы так:\n[tasklist-check] merged 4 QA traceability entries\n[tasklist-check] dropped 1 invalid progress entries\n[tasklist-check] rebuilt AIDD:NEXT_3","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
