 - `ProfileRoleService.java` — Role resolution with caching","     - `RbacConfig.java` — Component scan configuration","-  - DoD:","-    - Profile client fetches roles from profile service","-    - Caffeine cache stores roles with 5min TTL","-    - Cache invalidation on role change","-    - Fail-closed when profile service unavailable","+  - DoD: Profile client fetches roles, Caffeine cache with 5min TTL, cache invalidation works, fail-closed on errors","   - Boundaries:","     - No SSE events yet","     - Profile service URL configurable"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
